				<p>We may collect data necessary to process your payment if you choose to make purchases, such as your payment instrument number, and the security code associated with your payment instrument. All payment data is handled and stored by Stripe. You may find their privacy notice link(s) here: <a class="link link-primary" href="https://stripe.com/privacy">https://stripe.com/privacy</a>.</p>
				<h4 class="my-4">Social Media Login Data</h4>
				<p>We may provide you with the option to register with us using your existing social media account details, like your Facebook, X, or other social media account. If you choose to register in this way, we will collect certain profile information about you from the social media provider, as described in the section called "HOW DO WE HANDLE YOUR SOCIAL LOGINS?" below.</p>
				<p>All personal information that you provide to us must be true, complete, and accurate, and you must notify us of any changes to such personal information.</p>
